---
title: Italian Pork Meatball & Veggie Soup  with Parmesan Cheese
description: This warming soup is a bowl of pure Italian comfort, packed with a garden’s worth of veggies! The addition of savoury pork meatballs makes this dish extra hearty, and a sprinkle of Parmesan over the top gives just the right amount of rich cheesiness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65fbb32de1ef8615f8eef2c6-1a9b49f3.jpeg
